data.description: INVESTORS COME SEE!  2BR 2BA with garage and Florida room fixer-upper in Boynton's hottest Adult 55+ community.  Home is in need of extensive rehab, but potential is great. Florida room overlooking private backyard and a screened patio off kitchen, neutral tile thru-out. Large driveway can accommodate multiple cars. Avocado, mango and guanabana (''soursop'') trees.Short stroll to clubhouse, waterfront walking/biking paths. $158. monthly HOA fee includes cable tv/ internet and lawn watering. 238 residences in peaceful, lovely neighborhood is self-managed with healthy financials, and is well located to shopping, dining, highways, int'l airports and the BEACH. Lakefront clubhouse, heated pool, tennis/pickleball, billiards, boat ramp. Come make it your home and bring all of your pets!
